snippet.title: EA SPORTS UFC Mobile: Women’s Bantamweight Division Update
snippet.description:
The Women’s Bantamweight Division now playable in EA SPORTS UFC Mobile, featuring seven new fighters including Champion, Ronda Rousey. Download Now!

iOS: http://apple.co/1GkzsAc
Android: http://bit.ly/1ICQTKv
